        Now, meet Takashi Murakami, our local Japanese artist. He aims to create in-vogue hip-hop pieces. This artist is famous
        for multiple reasons, creating the cover pages of famous rappers as one of the reasons. But before his career took off,
        he specialized in abstract versions of anime jokes. Above, his piece called “The Octopus Eats His Own Leg” can be
        commissioned for R95,000.
